  "text": "Spatial clustering has been extensively studied [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . These approaches focus on generic methods to extract cluster information from large collections of ad hoc data points. Our clustering problem is more specific, since we deal with series of points ordered along 3D genes, and more importantly on the (potentially large) metadata associated to the 3D models.",
